Odaily Planet Daily News According to The Data Nerd, in the past 24 hours, multiple wallets have withdrawn 22.26 million WIF from CEX, equivalent to about 18.02 million US dollars. Specifically: 
The address starting with G1pif withdrew 2.68 million WIF, equivalent to about 2.1 million US dollars; 
The address starting with A3kTT withdrew 6.5 million WIF, equivalent to about 5.18 million US dollars; 
The address starting with D2Noa withdrew 4.08 million WIF, equivalent to about 3.38 million US dollars; 
The address starting with 4x3M8 withdrew 9 million WIF, equivalent to about 7.36 million US dollars.
